global j          -> move down
global down       -> move down
global k          -> move up
global up         -> move up
global g g        -> go to top
global G          -> go to bottom
global ctrl+d     -> half page down
global ctrl+u     -> half page up
global pgdn       -> page down
global pgup       -> page up
list   enter      -> open detail pane
list   space      -> open detail pane
list   /          -> search
list   ctrl+/     -> open keyboard shortcuts
list   ctrl+7     -> open keyboard shortcuts
list   c          -> create issue
list   s          -> set status
list   p          -> set priority
list   a          -> set assignee
list   ctrl+r     -> refresh
list   d          -> toggle sort direction
list   o b        -> open in browser
list   ctrl+n     -> next page
list   ctrl+p     -> previous page
list   L          -> log in / re-authenticate
detail c          -> comment on issue
detail o b        -> open in browser
popup  enter      -> confirm
form_nav ctrl+enter -> submit
form_nav alt+enter  -> submit
form_nav tab        -> next field
form_nav shift+tab  -> previous field
new_issue_picker enter      -> confirm
new_issue_picker m          -> assign to me
new_issue_text ctrl+enter -> submit
new_issue_text alt+enter  -> submit
new_issue_text tab        -> next field
new_issue_text shift+tab  -> previous field
comment_input ctrl+enter -> submit
comment_input alt+enter  -> submit
comment_input esc        -> cancel
search enter      -> confirm
search ctrl+c     -> clear query
search down       -> move down
search up         -> move up
search ctrl+n     -> next completion
search ctrl+p     -> previous completion
search ctrl+y     -> accept completion
search tab        -> complete forward
search shift+tab  -> complete backward
help   down       -> move down
